So it's been a little while... I sorta forgot about this thing.   Life has been really random and good and sort of not good for this past while.   For those who don't know, I'll list some key events  which could describe how things are going around here in a nutshell. 


Moved out of dads house.  Moved in with mom. Had an extended run in with "a bad crowd"  Moved out of moms house.  Dropped out of school.   Moved in with Michelle. Ceased to run with "bad crowd".  Had boyfriend for a while.  No longer have boyfriend.  Currently have job at Wendys.   Aunt  Mary Lou died of ALS(Lou Gerihgs(sp?) disease).  Don't want anything to do with mother.  Worried about the declining health of grandma.   Incredibly unsatisfied with how life is going for me in general at the moment...... etc.


Don't get me wrong though, I am a lot happier right now in general than probably ever before.  Yet, a lot of new and signifigantly more serious worries and problems have come up.  It really actually sucks not having parents to rely on...  its a kick in the ass when you realize, fuck, they really did a lot of shit for me... I have to do all that crap for myself now.  But damn if I'm going to give up and go running for help.  It's time to show everyone who ever said I couldn't do something or wouldn't amount to anything.  The big girl pants are gonna get put on, and all those motherfuckers are going to see that I don't need them.  I Will achieve everyhthing I planned for myself, by myself.  It might not happen right now, or even next week.  It might not even happen in a month.  Even so, I will work my ass off to make it happen, because I want it so bad.  It will feel so good, and I'll be like, damn right biatches!
http://liquidsubstance.livejournal.com/17485.html

Downloading music on my ipod... good fun.  I am really bored.  I also really miss some people very badly.  Hoping that they miss me too.  I need a C. really badly... like two maybe three.  But I have to wait... wait... patiently...  My feet are cold.

So I am home from Kentucky.  I'm glad I got an opportunity to go and see all my crazy family and whatnot.  Life is pretty good right about now.  Well anyway, only a limited amount of time left in OS till I go back to moms... so if you want to hang, call me.

I am really unhappy...  I don't think I am strong enough to take this.  If something doesn't change soon, a rash action may take place.

Right.... Yo yo homies.  So these past few days have been seriously kick ass.  Yesterday hung out with alyss and had tons of fun.  This morning Willis  came over and woke my ass up and we chatted for a good while.  Then later  me chell and kt hung out.  Played with kt's baby sister...  god I love babies.  Just got home like ten minutes ago.  I am home alone, as my father is in like Louisiana or somewhere for a few and a half days.  So my house is big and spooky and I'm all lonely.  If it were not midnight, I might just call somebody up and be all, wanna come stay the night.  Except it's midnight, so maybe not.  Don't know what lies in store for me tommorow, but I guess I'll find out.  Well I'm very sick feeling and tired, so I may go to bed.  Jennifer is out.

So I'm in town for the week.  Yay me.   


Brit: "I like playing with...."
Me:  "Nipples.... "

On baby bottles that is.   Pumpkin spice butter is really good.  Had a very fun afternoon with my brit-brit.  Tommorow should be awesome as well if it goes according to plans.  

On another note, I would like to apologize to someone.  You know who you are.  I love you like crazy and have missed you.  I'm really sorry that I have not been a good friend these past few...many... months.   

Final thought for the day:  Honky Tonkin!!

Hi everyone... just thought I'd drop you guys a line.  I am indeed alive and well.  Sorry I haven't really called or written to anyone, to those of you who care.   It's nothing personal at all.  Oh tommorow is my doggies 2nd birthday.  Yay for him.  Nos is a really awesome energy drink.. everyone should try it.  At any rate I have nothing more to say.  Miss you guys.  Love to everyone.  Jennifer

Soo.  I'm at alyssa's at the moment.  Today was tons of fun... cleaning al's room and moving furniture... hah not.  No I kid... it really wasn't that bad.   Saw pirates when it came out Thurs.  Yay for going to movies at Midnight.   Yeah I have been doing a lot of babysitting lately... thats all I do nowadays.  Babysitting tommorow morning as a matter of fact.   Hm, so there are some people, one in particular, that I thought I knew.  I thought they were one of my best friends.  But  as of lately I'm thinking not.  I'm so over it, really.  I'm sick of caring so much about people who don't care back.  It is taking so much out of me, so I throw in the towel... its over with.  Anyways... I'm missing the ending of A walk to remember... so I'm out.

Hrm....  my summer isn't totally going how it is supposed to.  But at any rate, I've checked off a lot of things on my summer to do list.  Exciting!  I've sort of almost mostly stopped biting my nails...  snaps for me... lol.    I finally got around to reading Angels and Demons; It was a good book.  I think The Da Vinci code still is a smidge better though.   Today is fathers day.  I gave my dad the gift that keeps on giving.. Space.  I stayed in my room as much as possible for the short amount of time I have been home.  Also I avoided talking to him whenever I could manage it.  Now that was the first and only present I've given my dad that he liked and didn't return, put in a dark drawer.... etc.   Not that he could have.  Anyways.   Off to go do... anything.

Somebody just shoot me right now.  How much longer do I have to endure the wrath....  not much longer actually.  I have to babysit tommorow.  I need to hang out with some people my own age the minute I get home.   Anybody call me....................... aaaaaaaaaghhghgghghhghghghghghsfsdahaaaaaaahgh.

Hey everyone... This was just an awesome day....   to much to explain, so I won't.  My day > your day... unless you are A.J.B, then your day was my day.  I love everyone!!  Now I am going to put myself to bed a little early.  

The moment I wake up
Before I put on my makeup
I say a little prayer for you
While combing my hair, now
And wondering what dress to wear, now
I say a little prayer for you

Forever, forever, you'll stay in my heart
And I will love you
Forever, forever, we never will part
Oh, how I'll love you
Together, together, that's how it must be
To live without you
Would only be heartbreak for me

I run for the bus, dear
While riding I think of us, dear
I say a little prayer for you
At work, I just take time
And all through my coffee break-time
I say a little prayer for you

Forever, forever, you'll stay in my heart
And I will love you
Forever, forever we never will part
Oh, how I'll love you
Together, together, that's how it must be
To live without you
Would only be heartbreak for me

I say a little prayer for you

Forever, forever, you'll stay in my heart
And I will love you
Forever, forever we never will part
Oh, how I'll love you
Together, together, that's how it must be
To live without you
Would only be heartbreak for me

My darling, believe me
For me there is no one
But you ....

Brittany and I got our hair cut today.  Her hair is ultra cute!!  Mine is okay... I have to get used to the shortness.   But when she came to get me this morning, of course I was sleeping.... she made me a smoothie though!!  Well in like a few  hours, there is a good chance I'm gonna go see that freaky omen movie with some people.  In the meantime, a nap is probably going to happen.  

Think Pink!!

Lets see, well, yesterday was ultra fun, so I have to document the goings on.  So around noon I went over to brittanys and molly was there, we swam and ate and had a good time all around.  Then  later chell came and kidnapped me.  She IRONED my hair... I think my tresses are melted together now, I should buy some deep conditioner to solve that.   We got to see our fathead Erica and her man.  That was more exciting than anyone knows.  So we all socialized and such stuff well into the night.  I almost killed me and chell on our way back home... it was so scary.   Then sandwiches... then  home at like twelve thirty.  Plus I imagine some other things went on, but I don't really recall.  Later we're gonna hang with the jew some more if she hurries up and finishes cleaning her Fema box.  Then much much later  alyss and I finally are going to have thai night, which we have been putting off for a considerable amount of time now.   OH... WELCOME HOME TIARA!!!!

P.s....  Anita Michelle White, you need to call me sometime in the very near future.  Like, now.

On another note, I really couldn't be anymore mad at my dad. Not so much mad, as... I don't know.  But he is making me want to cry and not stop.  Then I want to throw hard things at someones face.
